INSERT INTO businesses VALUES('13b6fa3b-1dab-480a-8274-ee30d5f61410','Bright Brothers Strategy Group','1311 W. Pasadena Ave, Phoenix, AZ 85013',33.51015730000000304,-112.0897913000000016,'(267) 6485798','https://www.bright-brothers.com/','other',1,'2024-01-01',1,'active','2025-08-11 18:48:31','2025-08-11 18:48:31','professional_services','marketing_advertising','Bright Brothers Strategy Group is a marketing and advertising agency specializing in placemaking, economic development, and MarCom. They work at the intersection of these fields, underpinning everything they do with qualitative metrics to ensure success for the communities they serve. Their unique approach involves making places ''pop'' and driving foot traffic, occupancy, and engagement in these areas. They serve a wide range of clients, from local communities to businesses, and distinguish themselves by their focus on community impact and measurable results.','["placemaking","economic development","MarCom services","community engagement","marketing strategy"]','placemaking, economic development, MarCom, qualitative metrics, community impact','completed','2025-08-24T10:44:23.454Z','firecrawl','{"locally_owned":true,"specialty_focus":"placemaking and community impact"}',NULL,NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO businesses VALUES('08997fe9-ff6d-457e-94bf-0ff2ff3b02b6','Bright Path Wellness','8701 E Vista Bonita Drive, Suite 110, Scottsdale, AZ 85255',33.49338533854096767,-111.9717280657712877,'(480) 629-8110','www.brightpathwellness.com','other',1,'2024-01-01',1,'active','2025-08-11 18:48:31','2025-08-11 18:48:31','health_wellness','alternative_medicine','Bright Path Wellness is an alternative medicine business located in Scottsdale, Arizona. They offer a variety of services aimed at treating chronic and acute pain, COPD, surgery and injury recovery, dental pain and infections, digestive issues, and other unresolved health conditions. Their unique approach combines traditional Chinese medicine, acupuncture, regenerative laser therapy, and functional medicine to provide personalized treatment plans for their patients. With over 35 years of experience in natural medicine, they are committed to restoring their patients'' health and vitality through diverse natural medicine solutions.','["acupuncture","regenerative laser therapy","acupoint injection therapy","laser acupuncture","functional medicine","non-invasive body contouring"]','acupuncture, functional medicine, regenerative laser therapy, chronic pain relief, digestive issues, natural medicine, COPD treatments, surgery recovery, injury recovery, dental pain, infections','completed','2025-08-24T10:22:07.141Z','firecrawl','{"locally_owned":true,"specialty_focus":"Combining traditional Chinese medicine, acupuncture, regenerative laser therapy, and functional medicine to treat a variety of health conditions"}',NULL,NULL,NULL);
